{"url": "http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2016/06/22/game-of-thrones-watermelon-carving_n_10613762.html", "date": "2016-06-22", "content": "Dessert is coming.\nIn the time-lapse video above,\u00a0Italian fruit carver extraordinaire Valeriano Fatica\u00a0transforms an ordinary watermelon into a totally sweet bust of the Night King from \"Game of Thrones.\"\nFatica says this particular carving took 18 hours from start to finish. And while the artist could have chosen any edible canvas -- he once crafted\u00a0the Joker from a pumpkin\u00a0-- the fleshy watermelon offers a fantastic depiction of the Night King's icy glare.Got a little something in your nose there.", "title": "Watch This Artist Carve A Watermelon Into The Night King From 'Game Of Thrones'"}